comments: Scott (PHI) moves laterally into the path of Vucevic (ORL) during the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Scott (PHI) establishes himself in a legal position in the path of Fournier (ORL) and makes marginal contact during the pick that does not prevent him from disengaging.
Vucevic (ORL) makes contact with Bulter's (PHI) foot as he is landing but contact is marginal and does not affect his ability to land safely.
Vucevic (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Butler (PHI) and gives him room to avoid contact.
Butler (PHI) maintains a legal guarding position on Vucevic (ORL) during the drive and cleanly dislodges the ball.
Harris (PHI) places a hand/arm to the front of Isaac (ORL) during the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
RLB shows as Vucevic (ORL) engages for the loose ball, he extends his leg and makes foot contact with the ball.
{Observable in Enhanced Video} Fournier (ORL) lifts his pivot foot.
Vucevic (ORL) makes marginal contact with Scott (PHI) off ball that does not affect his ability to defend the pass.
Vucevic (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Butler (PHI) and slightly extends his arm against him but he is able to move through contact.
Fournier (ORL) commits a take foul on Butler (PHI).
Fournier (ORL) makes contact with Harris' (PHI) side but does not affect his SQBR.
{Observable in Enhanced Video} Redick (PHI) slides his pivot foot after he picks up his dribble.
RLB shows Vucevic (ORL) makes contact to Redick's (PHI) arm during the drive that affects his ability to maintain control of the ball.
Augustin (ORL) commits a take foul on Harris (PHI).
Simmons (PHI) could be deemed to be imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Butler (PHI) makes contact with Vucevic (ORL) off ball that does not affect his ability to get to the pass.
Vucevic (ORL) commits a take foul on Harris (PHI).
Vucevic (ORL) briefly grasps Simmons' (PHI) arm but does not affect his ability to defend the shot in the post.
Fournier (ORL) commits a take foul on Butler (PHI).
